node.title: Four killed, eight injured after expressway bridge ramp collapses in central China
node.description: The collapse caused three trucks to fall and a car was crushed.
node.content: ["Four people were killed and another eight injured on Saturday (local time) when part of a bridge ramp collapsed in Ezhou City, in China's central Hubei province, the official Xinhua news agency reported.\n", "The bridge collapsed over an expressway, causing three trucks to fall while a car was crushed underneath, Xinhua reported, adding an investigation is underway.", "Work was being carried out on the bridge when the incident occurred, the report said."]
